究现状进行梳理 发现，目前学术界对新兴研究话题及其相关概念尚无清晰的界定；相应地，新兴研究话题的探测方法也存在诸多的不 足；探测新兴研究话题中所依据的指标繁杂多样。综述现有研究，本文给出新兴研究话题的概念及其特征的界定，比 较新兴研究话题及其相关概念的联系与区别，并指出在新兴研究话题发现中应注意的具体问题并提出四个方面的工作 展望。","tags":["Emerging Topic","Research Front","Emerging Topic Detection"],"title":"国外新兴研究话题发现研究综述","type":"publication"},{"authors":["Chao Lu","Yi Bu","Xianlei Dong","Jie Wang","Ying Ding","Vincent Larivière","Cassidy R. Sugimoto","Logan Paul","Chengzhi Zhang"],"categories":null,"content":"","date":1564617600,"expirydate":-62135596800,"kind":"page","lang":"zh","lastmod":1564617600,"objectID":"e224cde3b161a51a6e3b0d50042fdf7f","permalink":"https://luchao1991.github.io/zh/publication/lu-analyzing-linguistic-complexity-2019/","publishdate":"2020-02-11T03:53:17.641482Z","relpermalink":"/zh/publication/lu-analyzing-linguistic-complexity-2019/","section":"publication","summary":"","tags":["scientific writing","scientific impact","Syntactic complexity"],"title":"Analyzing Linguistic Complexity and Scientific Impact","type":"publication"},{"authors":["Chao Lu","Yi Bu","Jie Wang","Ying Ding","Vetle Torvik","Matthew Schnaars","Chengzhi Zhang"],"categories":null,"content":"","date":1556668800,"expirydate":-62135596800,"kind":"page","lang":"zh","lastmod":1556668800,"objectID":"e401da6a18ec023b925ee9ec9bd5c4c6","permalink":"https://luchao1991.github.io/zh/publication/lu-examining-scientific-writing-2019/","publishdate":"2020-02-11T03:53:17.634497Z","relpermalink":"/zh/publication/lu-examining-scientific-writing-2019/","section":"publication","summary":"","tags":["scientific writing","linguistic complexity","ethnic group","scientific collaboration"],"title":"Examining Scientific Writing Styles from the Perspective of Linguistic Complexity","type":"publication"},{"authors":["Chao Lu","Chengwei Zhang","Ying Ding","Dandan Ma","Yingyi Zhang"],"categories":null,"content":"","date":1546300800,"expirydate":-62135596800,"kind":"page","lang":"zh","lastmod":1546300800,"objectID":"2b5995188e4c0949fdec5e2d0b6d1fa9","permalink":"h